== Virtualenv init offline ==

Virtualenv bootstrap initial from fixed url:
    http://pypi.python.org/packages/source/d/distribute/.

If failed because of network issue, add a record in /etc/hosts:

    192.168.99.10  pypi.python.org

== Install pylons and related packages offline ==

* If using PIP, crate PIP config file: /root/.pip/pip.conf or
  pip.conf in this directory, point through $ENV["PIP_CONFIG_FILE"].

    [global]
    index-url = http://192.168.99.10/pypi/

* [obsolte] If using easy_install, check mirror config in /root/.pydistutils.cfg

    [easy_install]
    index_url = http://192.168.99.10/pypi/

* [obsolte] If using easy_install, pass PYPI environ for Makefile

    $ sudo PYPI=http://192.168.99.10/pypi/ ALLOWHOSTS=192.168.99.10 make all

== Virtual env initial ==

* make env                            : Virtualenv initial
* make pylons                         : Install pylons under virtualenv
* make all                            : make env + make pylons

== Create new instance ==
* ../bin/new_instance default : Create default instance.

